name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 4/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. This is the fluffy dog: The dazed child desired a companion amidst the strange life on the carnival grounds. Built with bits and bobs found at the edges, the dog is filled with nothing but innocence. Philosophers will ask themselves, does innocence make for a fool or a sage? Can a robot dog created by a dazed child from unknown refuse be either? And what of the love between dog and child? These robots are magical.
